[link: /commands/categories/expression.md] ’Щ@6ca18e1b3e0690539e59e0010072f59ac3d73b405fe9f8a65732301849968679ЩqTitle: title: polars when
Path: Signature
Content:
``> polars when {flags} (when expression) (then expression)``
’Щ@1a328ed2e5185ca185e5ee7d83560067b91a4a4d21036f81c1c54230f9259959Щ»Title: title: polars when
Path: Parameters
Content:
``when expression``
: When expression used for matching.
``then expression``
: Expression that will be applied when predicate is true.
