’Щ@556b991ea526f2fcd33113906a3ee614f29ea12d4c58d943114fc1ad5aa29670ЪсTitle: title: polars when
Path: Examples
Content:
Create a when conditions
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> polars when ((polars col a) > 2) 4


```
Create a when conditions
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> polars when ((polars col a) > 2) 4 | polars when ((polars col a) < 0) 6


```
Create a new column for the dataframe
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[a b]; [6 2] [1 4] [4 1]]
   | polars into-lazy
   | polars with-column (
    polars when ((polars col a) > 2) 4 | polars otherwise 5 | polars as c
     )
   | polars with-column (
    polars when ((polars col a) > 5) 10 | polars when ((polars col a) < 2) 6 | polars otherwise 0 | polars as d
     )
   | polars collect
